{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"af2454b626","title":"对共青团九大的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7737a30b25","index":0,"year":1964,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"af2454b626"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2426f89b62","type":"paragraph","text":"对共青团九大的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"09a4d88551","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"941eef05c5","type":"paragraph","text":"有为青年多得很，青年一代要打败老一代，我们的未来就是他们的，不要为名望、知识所惧怕，青年人要敢想、敢说、敢做、要从各种狭险的限制中解放出来。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"619b7829d0","type":"paragraph","text":"在计委镇导小粗汇报第三个五年计划时的一些插斋","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"69997acfe9","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年五月十一日）一、搞计划要把朝、越的一些需要打进去，听说越南要××万吨油二、一九六五年不一定有七亿二千万人口吧：一九七O有八亿？不得了。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"90e9e76b75","type":"paragraph","text":"三、知识分子很重要，没有不行。理论要知识分子，理论没有知识分子不行。但是知识分子还是要总结下面的东西。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"b22bdbe422","type":"paragraph","text":"四、国民经济的两个拳头，一个屁股。基础工业是一个拳头，国防工业是一个拳头，农业是屁股。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"f7b0eee054","type":"paragraph","text":"五、现在的苏联是资产阶级专政，大资产阶级专政，德国法西斯专政，希特勒式的专政，是一帮流，比高乐还坏六、所有的单位，工厂、街道、学校、机关都要划阶级。七、工资问题。再减上面的工资有困难。今后朵取上面不动，下面逐步增加的办法。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"58b82ca706","type":"paragraph","text":"八、工业为谁服务？工业要为农业服务。当然，重工业之间有一个相互关系问题，但是整个工业是为农业服务的·九、稳产、高产是相对的，去年河北大雨是天老爷下的，没有办法。天老爷难当，下多了不是，下少了也不是。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"d828eb8f6a","type":"paragraph","text":"十、有多少力，办多少事。不要以个人来决定。“我这个人老啦，快死啦，在我死以前，要千出什么....这不对。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"d270c418fb","type":"paragraph","text":"十一、我要把二十四史看完。《旧唐书》比《新唐书》好，《南史》、《北史》比《旧唐书》又好些，最不浦意的是《明史》。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"6a48d655d3","type":"paragraph","text":"十二、工厂划阶级的目的，在于暴露那百分之一、二、三、四、五，工人中不是工人阶级出身的有百分之八至十五。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"2101f81dbe","type":"paragraph","text":"111","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626"}],"page":{"id":"d5ffbb6cd6","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"af2454b626","start":124,"end":124}},"maoquanji46":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2b23c6dd81","type":"title","text":"对共青团九大的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"af2454b626"},{"id":"4e71d8ec11","type":"paragraph","text":"有为青年多得很，青年一代要打败老一代，我们的未来就是他们的，不要为名望、知识所惧怕，青年人要敢想、敢说、敢做，要从各种狭险的限制中解放出来","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"af2454b626"}],"page":{"id":"364d0c121b","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"af2454b626","start":387,"end":387}}}},"__N_SSG":true}